BBNaija lockdown housemate, Wathoni has declared no one will take her place on Bright O’s bed. Wathoni said she won’t let anyone sleep on the same bed with Bright O no matter what. Recall that Wathoni has recently shown interest in Bright O even though he isn’t giving her the green light. “Bright O, please just in case you have visitors, that’s my pillow on the right so help me throw it this way. That’s my space, ain’t nobody gonna take my space,” she said. Recall that Wathoni, Dorathy, and Bright O have been caught up in a love triangle. Bright O has however disclosed to Vee that he is not interested in any relationship.